    dc:creator "Valencia, Luis; Evans, Gregory A." ;
    dc:date "2024" ;
    dc:title "Review of the genus Tetralicia (Hemiptera: Aleyrodidae) and description of two new species of whiteflies found on avocado trees in Peru" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10561830>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10561840> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10561830>
    dc:description "PLATE 1. Puparia of aleyrodine genera. A) Aleuroclava aucubae, B) Aleurocanthus woglumi, C) Aleuroparadoxus iridescens, D) Aleurolobus marlatti, E) Hesperaleyrodes michoacanensis, F) Paraleurolobus chamaedoreae, G) Aleurocerus sp, H) Aleurothrixus floccosus (sms=submarginal setae), I) Aleurotrachelus tracheifer (smf=submedial furrow), J) Tetraleurodes mori, K) Aleurovitreus insignis, L) Crescentaleyrodes fumipennis, M) Crenidorsum aroidephagus, N) Aleurotulus mandururu, O) Aleurotuba jelinski, P) Aleuroplatus biluminiporus. Sources: A (USNM specimen); B, C, F, H, I, K, M, N (Martin, 2005); D (Regu & David, 1993), E (Sampson, 1943); G (Russell, 1986); J (Nakahara, 1995); L (Bondar, 1923); O (Mound, 1966), P (Martin & Malumphy, 2002)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10561830/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10561840>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Tetralicia ericae Harrison, 1917. (A–E) puparia: A) habitus drawing, B) habitus slide specimen, C) abdomen, D) vasiform orifice slide specimen, E) vasiform orifice drawing; (F–K) adult male: F) habitus, G–H) genitalia, I–K) antennae; (L–P) adult female: L) habitus, M–N) ovipositor; O–P) antennae. Sources: A, E, H, I, J, N (Bink-Moenen, 1989); B, C, D, F, G, K, L, M, P (USNM specimen)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10561840/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

